#

&nbsp;

![About](https://i.imgur.com/g8x3Mf2.png)

&nbsp;

*Cat Loaf* adds a new loafing position to your Minecraft cats. When you tell your cat to sit, there will be a 50% chance that it will sit like it normally does, and 50% chance that it will turn into a cat loaf.

&nbsp;
![Cat Loafing](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/813/424/cat_loaf.png)
&nbsp;
&nbsp;

This mod is required both on the **client side** and the **server side**, in order to properly synchronize and save the loaf status.

